whatever. we still love you, IQ!

Hey IQ i was wondering.Are you gonna be uploading the ENTIRE season 16 coming up in 720p ? If so i love you! If not i still love you for uploading this episode in high quality :D Its hard to come by stuff like this.Please reply.

I literally just made an account to say this, so I hope that is an indication of how awesome this is for me. 

It's hard to find proper HD uploads of this so I really hope you continue to do this with this series. :) Whether or not you decide to, thank you for this.

Thanks for the interest, but my capture equipment kinda failed me on today's episode so I figure I'll just stop encoding this instead of releasing sporadically. 


Also, Aquafox of Cartoon-World is releasing his 720p version of this series on their torrent tracker, so you can go ahead and check those out.

Tracking equipment fails, NOO. Well, looking at Cartoon World's uploads.. I can't quite put my finger on it, but the quality of your upload just seems considerably superior, and worth the larger size.

I appreciate your effort though, sorry the equipment gave you a bit of trouble.
Even if you are missing some of the episodes keep releasing them as i prefer yours over the others that are out there right now :)
